    process.getOutputStream().close();

You can also simplify the logic using `StringWriter` and try finally blocks. You shouldn&#39;t need `inheritIO`. Consider using file redirection `processBuilder.redirectOutput(File)` in case the sub-process writes a hugh mount of data to avoid OOM issues.

